Extract {{ target_count }} high-value insight highlights from the provided paper chunks.

Return strict JSON with this structure:
{
  "highlights": [
    {
      "chunk_index": 0,
      "quote": "Exact short quote from the chunk",
      "insight_summary": "Why this matters in one concise sentence",
      "confidence": 0.0
    }
  ]
}

Rules:
- Use only the chunk indexes provided.
- Keep quotes below 320 characters.
- Keep insight_summary below 220 characters.
- Confidence must be between 0 and 1.
- Prefer concrete, decision-relevant insights.

Chunks:
{% for chunk in chunks %}
- chunk_index={{ chunk.chunk_index }}: {{ chunk.text }}
{% endfor %}
